query_source_ok -  Check if the event has come from the valid source.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_source_ok(string event,
string source)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^event%^RESET%^ - the name of the event
%^BOLD%^source%^RESET%^ - the object trying to add the event
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
nonzero if the event can be added by the given source

.EI

